  </li>
  <li>
    <ref id="IEC61010-2">[IEC 61010-2:1998]</ref><p id="_4d04917f-970f-4e90-b340-0e4ab747a816">, <em>测量，控制和实验室用电气设备的安全要求 第2部分：加热材料的实验室设备的特殊要求， Safety requirements for electric equipment for measurement, control, and laboratory use — Part 2: Particular requirements for laboratory equipment for the heating of material</em></p>
